<ol>
<li>The normal rules of Diplomacy apply except where amended herein. 
<P><li>The standard Diplomacy map is used, with the single modification that
	Ruhr is a supply center.
<P><li>In addition to the normal Diplomacy powers, four new powers are
	added, making the game an eleven-player game.  These powers, and
	their home centers with their initial unit positions, are:
<center>
<table border>
<tr><th class=bodycopy bgcolor=#ff00ff><font color=white>Balkan</th>
